Title: An Act Transferring the Seat of Government of the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Sibutu Proper, Barangay Sibutu
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 57
An Act Transferring the Seat of Government of the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Sibutu Proper, Barangay Sibutu
Section 1. The seat of government of the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Taw-Tawi, is hereby transferred from Sitangkai Island to Sibutu Proper, Barangay Sibutu.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: February 1, 1980
